data.description: FHA ASSUMABLE AT 3.75%! Experience the true essence of peaceful living! This meticulously maintained home offers a harmonious blend of space, style, and tranquility. Step inside, and you'll be captivated by the open-concept design, where natural light beams through large windows, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. The spacious living area provides the perfect canvas for creating memorable gatherings by the cozy fireplace. The gourmet kitchen will inspire your culinary creations, boasting SS appliances, abundant cabinetry, and a convenient center island for meal preparations or casual dining. The lush backyard retreat is an idyllic sanctuary, inviting you to unwind on the covered patio while savoring picturesque views. The master suite, with its well-appointed en-suite bathroom, ensures your personal sanctuary for rejuvenation and relaxation. Don't miss this unbelievable opportunity to own your slice of country paradise.
